did.unittitle: International Brotherhood of Pulp Sulphite and Paper Mill Workers Records on Microfilm
did.abstract: These papers of the IBPSPMW cover most of the years from 1906, the year of the organization of the International Brotherhood, to 1957. Files for a few years are missing.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Microfilm copies of the files of the International Brotherhood of Pulp, Sulphite, and Paper Mill Workers.
This collection consists primarily of the President-Secretary's files.
